WEBVTT

01:51.590 --> 01:57.410
[The Legend of Rosy Clouds]

01:58.720 --> 02:01.920
[Episode 10]

02:02.380 --> 02:03.940
I'm back!

02:03.970 --> 02:05.280
Dad!

02:10.000 --> 02:11.150
Dad.

02:13.560 --> 02:15.710
Come take a look!

02:17.079 --> 02:17.960
Here.

02:20.150 --> 02:20.990
You lost!

02:21.010 --> 02:21.540
Drink up.

02:22.940 --> 02:23.590
Come on.

02:27.800 --> 02:29.660
When you leave the city tomorrow,

02:30.840 --> 02:32.960
make sure to find these women.

02:38.910 --> 02:39.800
Master.

02:40.470 --> 02:41.270
What's wrong?

02:43.120 --> 02:44.610
You work day and night.

02:44.630 --> 02:46.270
You really need to take a breather.

02:46.270 --> 02:47.300
How insolent!

02:48.200 --> 02:50.950
These women are bewitching the governor.

02:51.390 --> 02:52.150
That means

02:52.150 --> 02:55.390
Her Ladyship's been secretly dissatisfied
for a long time.

02:55.390 --> 02:56.220
We must

02:56.730 --> 02:58.130
teach them a lesson.

02:58.160 --> 02:59.280
-Yes.
-Go along.

02:59.300 --> 03:00.630
What were you thinking?

03:02.600 --> 03:03.560
My grandson.

03:03.590 --> 03:04.470
Grandfather.

03:06.280 --> 03:07.610
Time for your medicine.

03:08.780 --> 03:09.590
Grandfather?

03:31.829 --> 03:32.630
Grandfather.

03:33.730 --> 03:35.630
You were against
the governor and Her Ladyship's

03:35.630 --> 03:36.710
marriage.

03:37.120 --> 03:39.040
Now they're finally getting a divorce,

03:39.040 --> 03:41.500
why are you trying to
get them back together?

03:42.400 --> 03:44.000
A governor of the Nine Cities

03:44.579 --> 03:46.600
has never gotten a divorce before.

03:48.230 --> 03:50.690
As one of the Three Elders
in the Nine Cities,

03:50.960 --> 03:52.840
how can I just sit back and watch?

03:53.630 --> 03:55.370
Moral codes and etiquette can be

03:55.370 --> 03:57.060
destroyed by the slightest exception.

03:57.060 --> 03:59.540
We can't let them set this precedent.

04:03.080 --> 04:04.960
The precedent has already been set.

04:04.960 --> 04:06.150
As outsiders, do we really need

04:06.150 --> 04:08.480
to sincerely persuade them to reconcile?

04:09.630 --> 04:12.190
You make a good point.

04:17.740 --> 04:19.329
The crux of the issue is that

04:20.310 --> 04:21.209
Her Ladyship is

04:21.240 --> 04:22.440
unsatisfied

04:22.680 --> 04:25.360
with the governor's show of affection.

04:28.030 --> 04:28.910
How about this?

04:30.640 --> 04:31.790
Women

04:31.820 --> 04:34.330
like gifts the most,

04:34.350 --> 04:35.550
like jewelry.

04:35.580 --> 04:37.530
Tomorrow, go and pick

04:38.550 --> 04:41.060
a gift with a young man's taste,

04:42.350 --> 04:43.520
and present it

04:44.159 --> 04:45.220
as a peace offering

04:45.750 --> 04:47.240
on behalf of the governor.

04:48.740 --> 04:50.140
Perhaps,

04:50.170 --> 04:51.409
maybe,

04:51.430 --> 04:52.520
Her Ladyship will

04:52.550 --> 04:53.560
accept the apology.

04:53.560 --> 04:54.510
Me?

04:56.720 --> 04:59.050
You want me to make peace
for the governor?

05:09.990 --> 05:11.430
Do I really have to do it?

05:16.720 --> 05:17.240
Fine.

05:19.850 --> 05:21.460
OK. Sure.

05:38.370 --> 05:39.810
Your Excellency!

05:40.490 --> 05:41.310
Lord Zheng said

05:41.310 --> 05:42.480
we shouldn't come here again.

05:42.480 --> 05:43.680
Hu Die sent a secret letter

05:43.680 --> 05:44.920
asking us to come over.

05:44.920 --> 05:45.600
But...

05:46.500 --> 05:47.180
Wei Ying!

05:48.260 --> 05:49.310
[Song of the Oriole]

05:51.460 --> 05:52.290
Remove

05:52.320 --> 05:53.360
your head scarves

05:53.380 --> 05:55.180
for the gentlemen to have a look.

05:56.409 --> 05:57.290
Take them off!

05:58.770 --> 05:59.580
I...

06:09.720 --> 06:11.120
What happened?

06:11.480 --> 06:13.210
Weren't you fine the other day?

06:13.600 --> 06:14.310
So a beauty really

06:14.310 --> 06:15.850
doesn't rely on her hair and makeup.

06:15.850 --> 06:17.090
There is

06:17.120 --> 06:18.980
a distinctive charm to this look.

06:19.770 --> 06:21.500
These ladies woke up today

06:21.530 --> 06:23.090
to this crazy hair!

06:44.230 --> 06:45.190
Your Excellency,

06:45.190 --> 06:46.140
do you think

06:46.190 --> 06:47.740
we're being targeted?

06:47.820 --> 06:48.740
Right.

06:48.760 --> 06:51.020
They're even intimidating us like this.

06:51.040 --> 06:53.100
Who do you think would do such a thing?

06:57.400 --> 06:58.530
Who else could it be?

06:59.470 --> 07:00.820
It has to be Elder Zheng.

07:05.560 --> 07:06.850
But this is unexpected.

07:06.850 --> 07:08.510
He was so critical of Fan Yun back then,

07:08.510 --> 07:09.680
so we didn't even factor him in

07:09.680 --> 07:10.710
as a hurdle

07:11.680 --> 07:13.020
in the divorce plan.

07:17.240 --> 07:18.160
Why is he

07:18.160 --> 07:19.560
against the divorce now?

07:23.720 --> 07:24.980
Lord Zheng is entrusted

07:24.980 --> 07:26.750
by the former governor to assist me;

07:26.750 --> 07:27.690
to mold and restrain me

07:27.690 --> 07:29.620
as a role model for the Nine Cities.

07:29.650 --> 07:31.380
He would rather I be mediocre

07:32.400 --> 07:34.050
than be out of line.

07:40.930 --> 07:41.540
Let's go!

07:41.930 --> 07:43.130
To the Fan residence.

07:45.320 --> 07:47.250
-What about his... Yes.
-Let's go.

07:49.750 --> 07:50.880
Goodness!

07:50.900 --> 07:52.530
Who is it? So impatient!

08:00.630 --> 08:01.510
May I ask if you are

08:01.510 --> 08:02.270
Lord Fan Qi?

08:02.520 --> 08:03.160
I am.

08:03.720 --> 08:04.200
Who...

08:04.230 --> 08:05.430
Who might you be?

08:05.450 --> 08:07.090
I'm Lou Qiyan of Juyun Pavilion.

08:07.090 --> 08:08.740
On the order of Lord Zheng, I'm here to

08:08.740 --> 08:10.950
deliver apology gifts to Her Ladyship
on behalf of the governor.

08:10.950 --> 08:12.240
Juyun Pavilion?

08:13.790 --> 08:15.190
It's an honor to meet you.

08:16.230 --> 08:17.700
However, my stubborn daughter

08:17.700 --> 08:19.280
ran back home without permission.

08:19.280 --> 08:20.970
How could we accept gifts?

08:21.750 --> 08:24.020
Let me thank
the governor and Lord Zheng's kindness

08:24.020 --> 08:25.980
on behalf of my daughter.

08:26.520 --> 08:27.380
Please go back.

08:27.520 --> 08:28.400
Let me explain.

08:29.000 --> 08:30.700
Juyun Pavilion acts for money.
I don't want to

08:30.700 --> 08:32.870
get involved in the governor
and Her Ladyship's private affairs.

08:32.870 --> 08:34.990
I hope you accept the gifts,

08:35.010 --> 08:36.940
so I can complete this commission.

08:37.980 --> 08:39.690
Then tell Lord Zheng that

08:39.720 --> 08:40.600
I, Fan Qi,

08:40.620 --> 08:41.280
absolutely

08:41.280 --> 08:42.600
refused to accept them!

08:42.600 --> 08:43.690
Whatever happens,

08:43.720 --> 08:44.740
you're exempted from blame.

08:44.740 --> 08:46.340
That's it! Alright! Thanks!

08:48.550 --> 08:49.160
Alright.

08:50.520 --> 08:51.620
Smash all the gifts.

08:51.620 --> 08:52.310
Yes!

08:55.570 --> 08:56.970
Don't! Don't smash them!

09:01.460 --> 09:02.510
Don't. Stop.

09:04.600 --> 09:06.510
What a waste to smash them.

09:06.530 --> 09:08.130
It was unnecessary to bring gifts
on behalf of the governor.

09:08.130 --> 09:09.640
We'll just deal with it here.

09:09.640 --> 09:10.250
Keep smashing.

09:10.250 --> 09:11.180
Don't, don't...

09:11.230 --> 09:12.420
You can return them!

09:13.230 --> 09:14.320
What for?

09:14.340 --> 09:15.670
Lord Fan, you're right.

09:15.680 --> 09:17.460
These gifts are pointless to begin with.

09:17.460 --> 09:18.790
-They're an eyesore.
-Exactly.

09:18.790 --> 09:19.450
Smash them!

09:19.850 --> 09:21.060
When did I say that?

09:21.610 --> 09:22.280
I...

09:24.820 --> 09:25.540
Stop!

09:32.170 --> 09:33.880
This... This...

09:33.910 --> 09:35.630
What nice sesame flatbread!

09:35.630 --> 09:37.730
It's a pity to waste it. Goodness.

09:37.930 --> 09:39.650
The sesame flatbread isn't worth much.

09:39.650 --> 09:41.740
The sesame is fragrant.

09:41.770 --> 09:43.100
Fresh sesame.

09:43.420 --> 09:45.160
-It smells so good.
-Your Excellency.

09:45.160 --> 09:45.950
Your Excellency!

09:45.950 --> 09:46.610
We're here?

09:46.920 --> 09:49.050
Looks like someone got here before us.

09:51.110 --> 09:52.390
Look at this.

09:52.410 --> 09:54.370
Clearly made with fresh sesame.

09:55.680 --> 09:57.160
Him again?

09:58.720 --> 10:00.650
Looks like he's making a delivery.

10:03.510 --> 10:05.240
He's always pestering Fan Yun.

10:05.760 --> 10:07.760
I've been sick of him for a long time.

10:08.010 --> 10:08.540
Come.

10:09.030 --> 10:09.960
Help me get off.

10:10.710 --> 10:11.710
Your Excellency,

10:11.750 --> 10:12.440
you came today

10:12.440 --> 10:13.630
to discuss with Her Ladyship

10:13.630 --> 10:15.160
tomorrow's arrangements.

10:15.540 --> 10:16.800
If another conflict arises,

10:16.800 --> 10:18.330
it might be used against us.

10:20.720 --> 10:21.810
You have a point.

10:24.730 --> 10:26.520
Every grain of rice

10:26.540 --> 10:28.060
is hard-won.

10:29.160 --> 10:30.550
Stop smashing the gifts.

10:30.550 --> 10:31.730
Move them inside, please.

10:31.730 --> 10:32.570
They're all ruined.

10:32.570 --> 10:33.270
Let's forget about it.

10:33.270 --> 10:33.870
No, no, no.

10:33.890 --> 10:34.750
-Smash...
-No!

10:36.060 --> 10:37.060
Move them inside.

10:37.550 --> 10:38.430
Come on. Come.

10:38.460 --> 10:38.810
But...

10:38.810 --> 10:40.410
Please. Come in.

10:43.450 --> 10:44.090
Hey, look!

10:44.540 --> 10:46.400
The nerve of him to enter her home!

10:46.600 --> 10:47.470
-Your Excellency,
-Your Excellency,

10:47.470 --> 10:50.530
-it seems he was dragged in.
-it seems he was dragged in.

10:53.670 --> 10:55.520
I don't believe I can't keep you in check.

10:55.520 --> 10:56.450
I'm getting off!

11:06.840 --> 11:08.240
Please have some tea.

11:23.560 --> 11:24.290
Dad.

11:29.140 --> 11:29.730
Zheng...

11:32.670 --> 11:33.990
Young Master Qiyan,

11:34.280 --> 11:35.280
why are you here?

11:36.210 --> 11:36.920
Miss Fan,

11:37.390 --> 11:38.190
we meet again.

11:39.440 --> 11:40.570
You know each other?

11:42.550 --> 11:43.810
-I...
-I'm a merchant.

11:44.030 --> 11:45.970
I've heard a lot about Teacher Fan
from the private school

11:45.970 --> 11:47.030
across the street.

11:49.820 --> 11:50.620
That's right.

11:51.170 --> 11:52.720
The private school kids

11:52.750 --> 11:54.650
are the apple of Yun's eye.

11:54.780 --> 11:55.710
Well...

11:56.420 --> 11:57.420
Young Master Lou,

11:58.690 --> 11:59.780
is the tea

12:00.370 --> 12:01.800
to your liking?

12:06.620 --> 12:07.340
Dad.

12:24.820 --> 12:27.440
There are hundreds of teahouses
under my Juyun Pavilion,

12:27.440 --> 12:28.530
but none of them

12:28.550 --> 12:30.200
can brew tea like this.

12:32.470 --> 12:34.080
What does that mean?

12:34.100 --> 12:35.460
Is it

12:35.600 --> 12:36.980
good or bad?

12:37.370 --> 12:38.170
Exceptional.

12:41.400 --> 12:42.430
Exceptional.

12:43.320 --> 12:44.360
Well said.

12:44.380 --> 12:47.300
You're clearly an experienced merchant
who has seen the world.

12:47.300 --> 12:48.430
Young Master Lou was

12:48.450 --> 12:50.480
entrusted by Second Young Master Zheng

12:50.480 --> 12:51.390
to deliver

12:51.410 --> 12:53.250
the governor's

12:53.280 --> 12:54.440
apology gifts.

12:55.550 --> 12:56.200
It's up to you

12:56.200 --> 12:57.400
how we deal with them.

12:58.270 --> 12:59.230
I'll go

12:59.480 --> 13:00.700
boil more water

13:00.920 --> 13:02.010
so you can

13:02.030 --> 13:04.110
properly savor this tea.

13:06.910 --> 13:07.840
Exceptional!

13:10.630 --> 13:12.080
Did my dad just say

13:12.720 --> 13:13.630
the governor

13:14.330 --> 13:16.730
asked you to deliver these apology gifts?

13:16.850 --> 13:18.680
You grew up drinking such tea?

13:24.860 --> 13:25.860
Then I like it too.

13:26.130 --> 13:27.060
It's quite nice.

13:31.150 --> 13:32.510
Are you here today

13:33.030 --> 13:34.380
representing

13:34.630 --> 13:35.490
Juyun Pavilion

13:36.000 --> 13:37.360
or

13:37.600 --> 13:38.630
Lord Zheng?

13:41.480 --> 13:42.740
It's purely business.

13:44.320 --> 13:46.320
But I also have a personal question.

13:48.250 --> 13:48.950
What is it?

13:53.650 --> 13:54.870
Are you really set on

13:55.190 --> 13:56.390
getting the divorce?

14:02.870 --> 14:03.910
I'm afraid

14:05.150 --> 14:06.030
this isn't

14:06.030 --> 14:07.830
something you should be asking.

14:07.920 --> 14:09.520
I'm still his wife right now.

14:09.720 --> 14:10.910
Why use a title given by others

14:10.910 --> 14:11.970
to label yourself?

14:12.250 --> 14:13.160
You are you,

14:13.190 --> 14:14.590
not anyone's accessory.

14:15.150 --> 14:17.190
I heard someone is running errands
for my sake.

14:17.190 --> 14:18.850
Let me see who is so concerned.

14:19.360 --> 14:20.360
Your Excellency?

14:21.910 --> 14:23.270
So it's you.

14:26.000 --> 14:26.940
Did you bring

14:27.480 --> 14:28.740
all these things here?

14:29.010 --> 14:30.540
You know some manners, huh?

14:32.140 --> 14:33.870
Today, I'm Lord Zheng's envoy,

14:34.230 --> 14:36.560
here to share Your Excellency's burdens.

14:37.660 --> 14:39.460
You're Elder Zheng's grandson.

14:39.660 --> 14:40.890
I don't need his grandson

14:40.890 --> 14:42.800
to worry about my affairs.

14:46.740 --> 14:48.880
Since I, her rightful man, have arrived,

14:48.880 --> 14:50.260
if there's nothing else,

14:50.260 --> 14:51.790
you'd best take your leave.

14:53.090 --> 14:54.110
This is my home.

14:54.640 --> 14:55.970
Isn't your home my home?

14:58.630 --> 14:59.720
Still here?

15:00.190 --> 15:01.800
In that case, help me relay a message

15:01.800 --> 15:02.830
to Lord Zheng.

15:03.230 --> 15:04.490
Tell him that tomorrow,

15:04.490 --> 15:05.750
my wife and I will visit

15:06.550 --> 15:08.080
the Three Elders together.

15:17.000 --> 15:18.460
I shall take my leave then.

15:41.550 --> 15:43.150
Didn't we agree

15:43.170 --> 15:44.690
to get a divorce?

15:44.720 --> 15:46.120
Why'd you act all jealous just now?

15:46.120 --> 15:47.450
Now the fight we had was for nothing!

15:47.450 --> 15:49.250
All that acting was for nothing!

15:49.550 --> 15:51.240
I just don't like that fellow.

15:51.750 --> 15:52.680
You are my woman.

15:52.930 --> 15:55.000
Why is he acting so attentive to my woman?

15:55.000 --> 15:55.930
I won't allow it!

15:56.600 --> 15:57.290
I...

16:00.250 --> 16:01.520
I also think

16:01.950 --> 16:03.350
his motives aren't pure.

16:03.840 --> 16:04.920
Maybe

16:05.510 --> 16:07.070
he was sent by Lord Zheng

16:07.510 --> 16:08.630
to test us.

16:09.600 --> 16:11.490
You should have been colder just now,

16:11.490 --> 16:13.200
or just scolded me directly.

16:13.670 --> 16:14.930
That's the right move.

16:18.290 --> 16:18.910
Alright.

16:21.530 --> 16:23.130
I have something to give you.

16:25.480 --> 16:26.440
What is this?

16:27.880 --> 16:28.430
Hey...

16:29.460 --> 16:30.940
What is this?

16:31.490 --> 16:33.130
The divorce paper.

16:40.740 --> 16:41.750
We just

16:42.080 --> 16:43.910
barely mentioned it,
and it's already

16:43.910 --> 16:45.640
caused a scandal all over town.

16:46.390 --> 16:47.670
If we bring this divorce paper

16:47.670 --> 16:49.330
to the Three Elders tomorrow,

16:49.340 --> 16:51.340
and they still disagree, what then?

16:56.860 --> 16:59.060
I suppose the Three Elders want to see us

16:59.300 --> 17:00.960
to mediate a reconciliation.

17:01.600 --> 17:03.690
But as long as we convince them,

17:04.030 --> 17:05.490
we'll be close to success.

17:06.640 --> 17:08.300
I doubt it'll be that easy.

17:12.640 --> 17:14.130
We've had the fight,

17:14.160 --> 17:15.490
and we've put on the act.

17:16.200 --> 17:17.730
What else can we do?

17:20.680 --> 17:22.000
How about we

17:22.400 --> 17:23.599
get into a fist fight?

17:25.160 --> 17:26.819
That's really not necessary.

17:27.319 --> 17:28.640
We'll definitely

17:28.660 --> 17:30.550
think of a compelling reason.

17:32.200 --> 17:33.520
What reason?

17:33.660 --> 17:35.420
What options do we have?

17:36.570 --> 17:39.000
How can we make them agree...

18:00.330 --> 18:01.480
Your Excellency,

18:01.590 --> 18:02.900
I actually have an idea.

18:02.900 --> 18:04.230
They can't refute this.

18:06.130 --> 18:07.860
What crazy idea do you have now?

18:08.200 --> 18:09.030
To divorce me,

18:09.030 --> 18:10.830
do you have to go to such lengths?

18:16.270 --> 18:16.920
Fine.

18:17.400 --> 18:18.330
Tell me about it.

18:19.400 --> 18:20.890
You... Well...

18:21.830 --> 18:23.640
It won't work if I say it now.

18:24.180 --> 18:26.710
Just tell me how much pressure
you can handle.

18:28.350 --> 18:29.440
Pressure?

18:30.790 --> 18:32.550
I govern the Nine Cities.

18:33.640 --> 18:35.370
What do I carry on my shoulders?

18:35.600 --> 18:37.530
The weight of an empire!

18:37.920 --> 18:39.590
Is there anything I can't handle?

18:39.590 --> 18:40.870
Bring it on.

18:41.400 --> 18:42.580
So that means

18:42.710 --> 18:43.880
you agree?

18:45.270 --> 18:46.930
I can say whatever I want then?

18:50.150 --> 18:50.910
Great.

18:51.850 --> 18:53.090
Tomorrow's success

18:53.720 --> 18:55.110
hinges on this.

18:57.030 --> 18:58.820
They're finally willing to see us.

18:58.820 --> 19:00.230
Maybe this mediation

19:00.260 --> 19:01.810
will be a piece of cake.

19:02.740 --> 19:04.160
Zheng, you're really something.

19:04.160 --> 19:06.510
With just a few words,
you made the governor

19:06.510 --> 19:07.830
realize his folly.

19:08.550 --> 19:09.710
I'm adept at

19:10.170 --> 19:11.700
settling external affairs

19:11.720 --> 19:13.580
and pacifying internal turmoil.

19:13.640 --> 19:15.100
But in the future, please don't bother me

19:15.100 --> 19:16.820
with this kind of thing again.

19:27.120 --> 19:28.120
Your Excellency,

19:29.270 --> 19:31.350
I heard that your divorce

19:31.480 --> 19:33.460
has become the talk of the town.

19:33.850 --> 19:37.770
Today, I gathered the ministers
to help reconcile

19:38.300 --> 19:40.320
Your Excellency

19:41.180 --> 19:42.590
and Her Ladyship.

19:44.670 --> 19:45.670
Your Excellency,

19:46.810 --> 19:50.130
since Her Ladyship
moved into your residence,

19:50.160 --> 19:53.990
you two have been a match made in heaven.

19:54.800 --> 19:55.630
Her Ladyship

19:56.000 --> 19:57.830
fulfills her filial duties to the utmost

19:57.830 --> 19:59.890
and is highly praised for her virtue.

20:00.550 --> 20:01.950
May I ask Your Excellency

20:02.110 --> 20:04.530
why you want to divorce Her Ladyship?

20:12.190 --> 20:13.050
Your Ladyship.

20:13.260 --> 20:15.460
Since the wedding, His Excellency has

20:15.480 --> 20:18.010
visited the inner chambers
every day, right?

20:18.950 --> 20:21.320
He treats you with great adoration

20:21.340 --> 20:23.290
and sees you as an equal.

20:24.400 --> 20:25.030
May I ask

20:25.570 --> 20:27.410
why you want to

20:27.480 --> 20:29.030
divorce His Excellency?

20:38.150 --> 20:39.690
Lord Lyu, you're right.

20:40.440 --> 20:41.500
But since entering

20:41.850 --> 20:43.650
the Qi Residence,
I've also been

20:44.110 --> 20:45.270
deliberating day and night

20:45.270 --> 20:47.390
about how to better serve the governor.

20:47.390 --> 20:48.460
But the governor

20:48.480 --> 20:50.170
is always moody.

20:50.200 --> 20:53.200
I've become a punching bag for him
to vent his anger on.

20:56.590 --> 20:57.580
Well...

20:57.610 --> 20:59.090
It's like this.

21:01.550 --> 21:02.640
His Excellency

21:02.880 --> 21:05.240
governs the Nine Cities after all.

21:06.400 --> 21:08.400
Moreover, this year, there have been

21:08.400 --> 21:09.720
quite a few disasters.

21:10.680 --> 21:11.550
The governor is

21:11.550 --> 21:13.820
devoted to official duties all day,

21:14.010 --> 21:16.540
so he inevitably
worries a lot for the people.

21:17.830 --> 21:20.110
By the time he returns home,

21:20.110 --> 21:22.170
he's bound to be a bit temperamental.

21:22.890 --> 21:24.150
Don't take it to heart.

21:26.350 --> 21:28.510
Spouses don't hold grudges overnight.

21:28.510 --> 21:31.170
Not to mention
these are all trivial matters...

21:31.830 --> 21:33.890
It's best for Your Ladyship to return

21:33.960 --> 21:35.020
to the Qi Residence

21:35.200 --> 21:36.330
as soon as possible.

21:36.610 --> 21:37.960
Yes, yes.

21:40.240 --> 21:41.700
Do you really want to know?

21:42.310 --> 21:43.200
Of course.

21:43.880 --> 21:46.790
The governor's divorce is a major affair.

21:49.160 --> 21:50.360
Everyone in the world

21:50.950 --> 21:52.880
is waiting for an answer.

21:57.310 --> 21:58.640
I thought I should avoid

21:59.200 --> 22:00.330
making such remarks

22:00.650 --> 22:02.520
out of respect for the governor.

22:03.570 --> 22:05.330
Now it seems...

22:06.770 --> 22:08.900
I have no choice but to come out with it.

22:12.160 --> 22:13.560
I forgot to tell you

22:13.850 --> 22:15.710
I can't handle any more pressure.

22:18.570 --> 22:20.300
Don't worry, Your Excellency.

22:24.350 --> 22:25.400
The reason is that

22:26.310 --> 22:27.270
the governor...

22:29.150 --> 22:30.320
His Excellency...

22:31.960 --> 22:33.220
can't function in bed.

22:35.150 --> 22:36.430
-What?
-What?

22:37.260 --> 22:38.550
What do you mean?

22:40.570 --> 22:41.180
He...

22:42.920 --> 22:44.500
can't function at all.

23:03.090 --> 23:04.770
He can't function at all?

23:07.800 --> 23:10.410
This embarrassment is too much to bear.

23:11.640 --> 23:12.920
After Her Ladyship's remarks,

23:12.920 --> 23:14.870
who'd still dare to
urge them to reconcile?

23:14.870 --> 23:15.500
Exactly.

23:16.510 --> 23:17.040
Zheng,

23:17.280 --> 23:20.440
all the ministers in the Qi Residence
are watching the three of us.

23:20.440 --> 23:21.570
Listen to me.

23:21.920 --> 23:23.780
Be it the youngsters' ignorance,

23:24.420 --> 23:26.230
or if they have other ideas,

23:27.030 --> 23:28.880
or if he can function or not,

23:30.000 --> 23:31.940
with Lord Jiang Shu here,

23:32.180 --> 23:34.270
I doubt they'd dare to talk nonsense.

23:34.930 --> 23:35.880
Lord Jiang.

23:37.030 --> 23:37.690
Lord Jiang,

23:38.310 --> 23:40.840
you're the best physician
in the Nine Cities.

23:40.920 --> 23:42.180
We're counting on you.

23:45.270 --> 23:46.200
I understand.

23:48.670 --> 23:49.470
Please.

24:17.200 --> 24:18.200
Your Excellency.

24:18.410 --> 24:20.340
-You're awake.
-Your Excellency.

24:21.830 --> 24:22.400
He...

24:32.300 --> 24:33.450
Who are you?

24:37.270 --> 24:39.830
Could it be that His Excellency is
traumatized by the verbal abuse

24:39.830 --> 24:41.360
in the main hall yesterday?

24:42.720 --> 24:43.580
Your Excellency,

24:43.580 --> 24:44.760
the issue hasn't been resolved.

24:44.760 --> 24:46.620
Feigning memory loss is useless.

24:47.440 --> 24:48.200
Eight.

24:48.510 --> 24:50.040
-Ten.
-That unconvincing?

24:52.080 --> 24:53.050
Get your fingers out of my face,

24:53.050 --> 24:54.310
or I'd really go blind.

24:54.850 --> 24:55.770
Help me up.

25:00.320 --> 25:01.360
Put my shoes on.

25:03.080 --> 25:05.010
You two are the absolute best to me.

25:06.610 --> 25:07.340
Look at this.

25:13.600 --> 25:14.640
What is all this?

25:14.660 --> 25:16.920
These are all tonics from the officials.

25:18.890 --> 25:20.090
Let's put it this way:

25:20.110 --> 25:22.470
as the governor and his wife
clamor for divorce,

25:22.470 --> 25:24.320
all the tigers in the Nine Cities

25:24.340 --> 25:25.380
had to suffer.

25:26.210 --> 25:27.140
Are you serious?

25:35.940 --> 25:37.200
Forgive me for my sins.

25:40.720 --> 25:42.810
What are you doing?

25:46.380 --> 25:48.240
-Your Ladyship!
-Your Ladyship!

25:52.130 --> 25:53.240
We'll take our leave.

25:53.240 --> 25:53.800
Don't go!

25:54.090 --> 25:55.090
Enjoy the tonics.

25:55.870 --> 25:57.070
Let's get out of here.

26:02.070 --> 26:03.070
Your Excellency.

26:03.880 --> 26:04.960
Your Excellency!

26:05.350 --> 26:06.110
Are you mad at me?

26:06.110 --> 26:07.030
Of course I am!

26:09.480 --> 26:10.600
Your Excellency!

26:10.690 --> 26:11.970
I only said that

26:12.000 --> 26:14.640
because you said
you could bear immense pressure.

26:14.640 --> 26:16.520
Otherwise, I wouldn't have said it.

26:16.520 --> 26:17.050
Yes,

26:17.530 --> 26:18.640
I did say

26:18.670 --> 26:19.820
I could bear the pressure,

26:19.820 --> 26:21.510
but I didn't say I could bear slander!

26:21.510 --> 26:22.240
And couldn't you

26:22.240 --> 26:23.550
have found a better excuse?

26:23.550 --> 26:24.350
Why did you...

26:24.540 --> 26:25.620
resort to that!

26:26.880 --> 26:28.030
Don't worry.

26:28.030 --> 26:29.740
I just made up an excuse.

26:30.120 --> 26:31.800
It doesn't mean it's true.

26:31.820 --> 26:32.760
What I say doesn't affect

26:32.760 --> 26:34.090
your bodily functions,

26:34.090 --> 26:34.670
am I right?

26:34.670 --> 26:35.460
But now...

26:36.000 --> 26:37.000
Don't be mad...

26:37.570 --> 26:38.180
Your Excellency,

26:38.180 --> 26:39.250
the Three Elders are here.

26:39.250 --> 26:40.940
Lord Jiang Shu is also here.

26:43.100 --> 26:45.570
Quick! Quick!

26:45.880 --> 26:46.960
Not Lord Jiang!

26:46.960 --> 26:48.890
W-Wouldn't we be exposed then?

26:54.830 --> 26:55.960
Greetings, Elders.

27:02.000 --> 27:03.660
Greetings, Your Excellency.

27:12.980 --> 27:13.940
Elders,

27:13.970 --> 27:15.170
His Excellency...

27:15.880 --> 27:17.590
passed out from exhaustion.

27:17.920 --> 27:19.520
-Lord Jiang.
-He passed out?

27:19.890 --> 27:21.270
Do what you need to do.

27:25.640 --> 27:26.640
L-Lord Jiang!

27:27.720 --> 27:28.610
Today,

27:28.640 --> 27:30.580
the governor is really not feeling well.

27:30.580 --> 27:32.720
We couldn't wake him up
no matter how hard we tried.

27:32.720 --> 27:33.460
Why don't we

27:33.480 --> 27:35.480
-do this another day...
-It's fine.

27:35.800 --> 27:37.360
I must take his pulse

27:37.380 --> 27:38.900
to know what's going on.

28:11.160 --> 28:12.000
Lord Jiang,

28:12.490 --> 28:13.750
how is His Excellency?

28:16.580 --> 28:17.260
It's over.

28:19.720 --> 28:20.680
What's over?

28:28.150 --> 28:30.320
Your Ladyship was telling the truth.

28:33.510 --> 28:34.320
What?

28:35.990 --> 28:36.840
This...

28:37.320 --> 28:38.510
L-Lord Jiang,

28:38.540 --> 28:41.220
are these tiger penises
and bear galls useless?

28:41.240 --> 28:42.040
Are they?

28:42.570 --> 28:45.570
Even dragon livers and phoenix brains
wouldn't work.

28:51.400 --> 28:52.390
Miss Fan,

28:53.900 --> 28:55.010
it seems

28:55.040 --> 28:56.620
this is a tricky situation.

28:58.020 --> 29:00.550
I'd advise you to
go through with the divorce.

29:01.170 --> 29:01.930
But...

29:02.570 --> 29:03.480
Then...

29:44.960 --> 29:45.960
Your Excellency!

29:46.270 --> 29:47.730
Your... Your Excellency!

29:50.030 --> 29:51.030
Your Excellency,

29:51.440 --> 29:52.970
don't take things too hard.

29:58.210 --> 29:59.750
I'm sorry. I really am.

30:00.110 --> 30:01.350
Y-You know

30:01.350 --> 30:03.110
I really just made up an excuse

30:03.110 --> 30:04.920
to fool the Three Elders.

30:04.920 --> 30:05.720
Who knew

30:05.720 --> 30:06.920
you actually really

30:06.940 --> 30:09.400
-can't function...
-Fan Yun, stop talking.

30:11.220 --> 30:12.820
I want to be alone for a while.

30:19.270 --> 30:20.270
Your Excellency,

30:20.870 --> 30:22.180
don't be afraid.

30:22.210 --> 30:23.710
Dysfunctions can be treated.

30:23.710 --> 30:24.840
I don't believe

30:24.870 --> 30:25.910
there's no one

30:25.960 --> 30:27.890
who can cure you in this vast world!

30:27.920 --> 30:29.160
I'm not ill!

30:39.260 --> 30:40.540
Your Excellency,

30:41.070 --> 30:42.480
please, I'm begging you.

30:42.790 --> 30:44.850
Don't just sulk alone and shut me out.

30:45.270 --> 30:46.360
How about we

30:46.390 --> 30:47.670
go to Lord Jiang

30:47.690 --> 30:48.950
and ask him for medicine?

30:48.950 --> 30:50.560
Maybe after a few doses,

30:50.680 --> 30:51.640
you'll be fine!

30:52.270 --> 30:53.270
Your Excellency.

30:57.900 --> 30:58.900
Your Excellency.

31:00.000 --> 31:01.480
Trust me.

31:02.120 --> 31:03.850
This can definitely be cured.

31:04.290 --> 31:05.720
I'm sure of it.

31:06.480 --> 31:08.110
Absolutely.

31:09.680 --> 31:11.210
Say something, Lord Jiang.

31:11.510 --> 31:13.830
The governor has arrived!

31:13.830 --> 31:15.160
The governor is here.

31:15.750 --> 31:18.510
Welcome, Your Excellency.

31:24.100 --> 31:25.610
You may rise, my dear ministers.

31:25.610 --> 31:27.890
Thank you, Your Excellency.

31:29.850 --> 31:31.580
My Lady spread rumors about me.

31:33.200 --> 31:34.030
The divorce

31:34.510 --> 31:35.590
is set in stone.

31:36.480 --> 31:37.720
Effective immediately,

31:37.720 --> 31:40.020
she'll resume her status
as a member of the Fan household

31:40.020 --> 31:41.820
and move out of the Qi Residence.

31:44.660 --> 31:45.460
You may leave.

31:48.200 --> 31:50.460
We will take our leave, Your Excellency.

31:56.960 --> 31:58.440
Proclamation from the governor:

31:58.440 --> 32:02.570
"Although Her Ladyship is virtuous
and devoted to marital duties,

32:02.680 --> 32:04.960
due to incompatible personalities,

32:04.980 --> 32:06.420
we are divorcing.

32:06.750 --> 32:08.080
From this day on,

32:08.100 --> 32:11.210
she'll resume her status
as a member of the Fan household.

32:11.210 --> 32:12.470
End of proclamation."

32:12.550 --> 32:14.570
This is the first divorce of a governor.

32:14.570 --> 32:15.900
Divorcing the governor

32:15.920 --> 32:17.290
is unheard of.

32:17.310 --> 32:18.420
Exactly.

32:18.450 --> 32:19.580
But I heard that

32:19.600 --> 32:22.750
the governor seems to have some issues.

32:23.060 --> 32:24.150
What issues?

32:24.540 --> 32:25.670
Don't ask too much.

32:28.000 --> 32:29.080
Yeah.

32:29.100 --> 32:30.500
I heard about it too.

32:31.790 --> 32:34.350
What will become of our Nine Cities now?

32:34.380 --> 32:35.380
I know, right?

32:40.960 --> 32:41.890
Fan Yun, are you

32:41.910 --> 32:44.170
taking these pieces of jewelry with you?

32:45.720 --> 32:46.350
Nope.

32:46.910 --> 32:48.310
I'll just take some

32:48.400 --> 32:49.860
stuff I brought from home.

32:50.400 --> 32:52.400
I'll leave everything else here.

32:54.100 --> 32:55.470
Are you really leaving?

32:56.600 --> 32:58.130
Yes, it's as real as it gets.

32:58.840 --> 33:01.440
Besides, the governor's proclamation
has been issued.

33:01.440 --> 33:02.900
I've been here for so long.

33:03.310 --> 33:04.270
I miss home too.

33:05.020 --> 33:06.420
The governor sure is ruthless.

33:06.420 --> 33:07.730
He's clearly at fault,

33:07.750 --> 33:09.210
yet you're the one to suffer.

33:09.210 --> 33:10.940
This has nothing to do with him.

33:11.680 --> 33:13.200
This is all my idea.

33:15.600 --> 33:16.430
Anyway,

33:17.310 --> 33:18.280
for me,

33:18.640 --> 33:19.900
leaving the residence

33:20.480 --> 33:21.420
is a good thing.

33:22.110 --> 33:23.310
After all this time, have you

33:23.310 --> 33:24.400
not caught any feelings

33:24.400 --> 33:25.730
for the governor at all?

33:42.240 --> 33:43.090
From now on,

33:43.790 --> 33:44.850
he's the governor,

33:46.390 --> 33:47.520
and I'm his subject.

33:49.300 --> 33:51.030
You didn't answer my question.

33:51.950 --> 33:52.670
Forget it.

33:53.600 --> 33:54.530
Anyway, the governor

33:54.530 --> 33:55.990
is used to a life of leisure

33:57.110 --> 33:58.530
and has no interest in politics.

33:58.530 --> 34:00.390
I don't think he's your cup of tea.

34:00.920 --> 34:01.790
Actually,

34:02.960 --> 34:03.880
the governor

34:03.880 --> 34:05.270
isn't like what you see.

34:06.550 --> 34:07.920
When the time is right,

34:08.590 --> 34:09.380
I believe

34:09.920 --> 34:11.690
the world will see the real him.

34:12.400 --> 34:13.530
Then, everyone will

34:14.250 --> 34:15.210
understand

34:15.840 --> 34:17.389
his painstaking efforts.

34:19.080 --> 34:20.080
I get it.

34:20.100 --> 34:21.780
Friendship remains even if the deal fails.

34:21.780 --> 34:23.780
You sure know how to speak up for him.

34:26.710 --> 34:27.590
Anyway,

34:29.280 --> 34:29.989
Miss Wei,

34:30.300 --> 34:32.400
thanks for taking care of me
during my stay.

34:32.400 --> 34:33.770
I owe it to you that

34:33.800 --> 34:35.330
everything went smoothly.

34:35.739 --> 34:36.409
Thank you.

34:40.940 --> 34:42.030
I'm sad that I won't

34:42.230 --> 34:43.790
get to see you here all the time

34:43.790 --> 34:45.020
from now on.

34:53.670 --> 34:54.380
Work is over.

34:54.380 --> 34:56.380
Aren't you going back, Captain Gao?

34:56.670 --> 34:57.520
You fellows go ahead.

34:57.520 --> 34:58.720
Then we'll get going.

35:00.400 --> 35:01.280
Miss Wei.

35:21.300 --> 35:23.090
You walked up to me yourself.

35:25.180 --> 35:25.980
What's wrong?

35:28.530 --> 35:30.660
Fan Yun is returning home
tomorrow morning.

35:30.660 --> 35:31.800
I'm feeling down.

35:32.560 --> 35:33.670
Is it OK if we talk?
